1.Open Xampp control Panel
2.Start both the Apache server and mySQL database(phpmyadmin)

The first page is the login page which is seperate for managers and customers.(login.php or loginserv.php)
Or alternatively one can start the intro page and choose their required login page.

Data is collected from the forms in each page and the data is stored in a database called:"what"
Any operations that need to be performed on data will be perfomed on the data stored in this database.

Built entirely using HTML,CSS for front-end and PHP,mySQL for backend
